				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Chu-ti%E1%BB%81n-ti%E1%BB%83u-nga-nhi/poem--sKwwuC3d3TUT_4-bJenwg">Chu tiền tiểu nga nhi - 舟前小鵝兒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/H%E1%BB%99i-ch%C3%A2n-thi/poem-LeoeJ0FsHz3zUPXXvFeE_g">Hội chân thi - 會真詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/Kh%E1%BB%95-h%C3%A0n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-RCqLASJqmsSdlQ17Wgji2w">Khổ hàn hành - 苦寒行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%A1t-Li%E1%BB%85u/poem-xdpmxMrS5eWC5GOr-k4MCg">Tần Cát Liễu - 秦吉了</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Th%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Song-h%E1%BA%A1c-c%C3%A2u-vi%E1%BB%85n-du/poem-jhzWhOCqQ-cwGTcTb0YzGw">Thất đề - Song hạc câu viễn du - 失題－雙鶴俱遠遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/Thu-H%E1%BB%93-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-ABKEkE4oaW6QbVVB-MWgjg">Thu Hồ hành kỳ 2 - 秋胡行其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-GsXnC9PxsLf4SLPkjq9THg">Thuật cảm - 術感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-k7nDOMHcGKaZoky6ue8-ag">Nguyễn Thượng Hiền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ph%C3%A1c/Tr%E1%BA%A7m-tu%C3%BD-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-phong-Ng%C6%B0-phu-song-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u/poem-dCycIFYUca9GFSFnFDoo_A">Trầm tuý đông phong - Ngư phu (song điệu) - 沉醉東風－漁夫（雙調）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ph%C3%A1c/author-6WbYdtzdi93NI7sjD0SLkg">Bạch Phác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%C4%A9nh/V%E1%BB%8B-th%C3%AA-t%C3%A1c-sinh-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%C3%BD-%C3%BD/poem-kODCpGEfWjo_G2eysclnHQ">Vị thê tác sinh nhật ký ý - 為妻作生日寄意</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%C4%A9nh/author-FLeQSz8PiNWt7aZh3N_djw">Lý Dĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-my-ho%E1%BA%A1-li%E1%BB%85u-t%C3%BA-li%C3%AAm-khai/poem-iQbSCVFuhI2XVWlEFLMeRw">Vô đề (Trường my hoạ liễu tú liêm khai) - 無題（長眉畫了繡簾開）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
